            <thetext>Move the event handling of qooxdoo in a separate layer and isolate it from the widget/ui code.

Goals for the new event layer:
  - unify event handling across browsers
  - unified interface to the event objects
  - event objects should be singletons
  - special key and mouse event handler
  - unobstrusive -&gt; existing event handlers should not be overwritten. Is should be possible to add custom event handlers without removing the qooxdoo handler
  - no dependencies to the qooxdoo widget system
  - integrate with html2.Element</thetext>
          </long_desc>
